biography:
Buy. Sell. Discover Unique Fashion.
Designer. Preloved. Vintage. Streetwear. Sneakers. Whatever your style. Find it on Depop.

node.text:
Whether they're shooting a fashion editorial or listing clothes on #Depop, breaking the gender binary is what continues to inspire @danielroaart – both personally and professionally. Here, the multi-talented photographer takes us with them on a typical day living and working in NYC.

Photographer - @danielroaart 
Stylist - @angelemmanuel 

Model - @cod.max 
Model - @champagnesocialist21
Model - @titusstwin

node.text: we celebrate and support Black creativity in its limitless forms – and believe that one of the best ways to show your support is to pay for it. We worked with LA-based photographer @mattcwen, editor @rickyrxse and music artist @fka_tweaks to spotlight @bbykamkam, @kennatree, @tajzon and @samonezena, a group of creatives who are paving the way for a future where every person can thrive – no matter who they are. Watch the full IGTV video now.

node.text: From her success as an artist to her blossoming directorial career, @iceicebabyspice is creating fantasy worlds for us to escape to. She chatted to us about her enviable handbag collection, her bright and colourful personal style and why she loves selling on #Depop.

node.text:
We shared our platform with API+ champions  @mimizhuxiyuan and @reignofdynasty to learn about community empowerment, connecting with grassroots movements and how to find courage in creativity. 

#APIHeritageMonth #StopAsianHate

The opinions expressed during this conversation are solely those of the individuals involved.

node.text: She’s a multi-talented pop artist, yes – but @stefanicolvin is exploring more than one creative avenue. From her self-styled music videos to her effortlessly cool, ‘00s-inspired Depop shop, Stef shares the projects she's most passionate about and takes us behind the scenes on a typical #Depop day.
